<br />\n廿年前QM已經好撚多乜鳩支那研究助理睇病開葯架啦！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96c9908cb0843df05ebfeb96cdefff55f7eb0b3","tid":101487,"uid":38672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加學位先可以解決問題</blockquote><br />\n加學位都要等班讀醫既學生畢業，大大話話都要等6-7年。正苦應該增加資源比醫院，吸引私家醫生回流。但個on9正苦居然調轉去cut budget，比班支那醫生黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府咁做好明顯係想整個藉口引入內地醫生 <br />\n續步將香港唔同行業大陸化<br />\n到時香港唔同行業都有班大陸人控制住<br />\n<br />\n另外而家普教中越來越多<br />\n下一代應該會比較親中<br />\n如果我地呢代反抗唔到就唔會再有機會<br />\n大家自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2872399c48de078d2d864811bab3a7a4ab9afd9","tid":101487,"uid":70531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加學位先可以解決問題</blockquote><br />\n加學位都要等班讀醫既學生畢業，大大話話都要等6-7年。正苦應該增加資源比醫院，吸引私家醫生回流。但個on9正苦居然調轉去cut budget，比班支那醫生黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實已經加緊<br />\n今年畢業嗰班都仲係每間大學~150個<br />\n到2018定19年畢業嗰班已經係每間大學&gt;200個<br />\n之後好似會愈黎愈多<br />\n遲下請晒啲大陸人又請唔晒啲本土醫學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90a922cbac1fe30337bfae22b7d00b4a366c7cb","tid":101487,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:15:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>世紀丈發現！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廿年前QM已經好撚多乜鳩支那研究助理睇病開葯架啦！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/